FBIS4-60787 "drsov084_m_94005" FBIS-SOV-94-084 Daily Report 30 Apr 1994 Tajikistan Edict on Celebration of Victory Day, 2-9 May Edict on Celebration of Victory Day, 2-9 May LD3004145094 Dushanbe Radio Tajikistan Network in Tajik 0030 GMT 30 Apr 94 LD3004145094 Dushanbe Radio Tajikistan Network Tajik BFN [Text] The edict of the presidium of the National Assembly of the Republic of Tajikistan on celebration of Victory Day: (1) To permit holding festivities dedicated to Victory Day from 2 to 9 May 1994, as an exception in conditions of the state of emergency in Dushanbe city and other areas of the republic where the state of emergency is declared. (2) The Ministries of Internal Affairs, Security, and Defense of the Republic of Tajikistan are to strictly ensure the public order and security and safety of citizens in the festive areas. (3) The edict comes into force from the day of its issue. [Signed] Emomali Rakhmonov, the Chairman of the National Assembly of the Republic of Tajikistan.
